{"tid":335031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地商生意跌30% 歸咎讀者只買繁體 籲加強簡體教育","createTime":"2017-07-25T09:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T14:42:57.000Z","uid":42804,"like":3,"dislike":277,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc8b728dc059eafbceeb5524ee5dc49b86a323ea","tid":335031,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:17:17.000Z","msg":"午飯過後越來越多市民入場書展，有大書商指已成功收復失成，生意與去年持平。三聯書店副經理高先生表示，首兩日少人入場及颱風停市半日對銷情有負面影響，但昨日延長開放時間有助追回生意，令整個書展表現可與去年持平。<br />\n<br />\n萬里機構總經理朱素貞亦指出，颱風日書展重開後市民反應踴躍，昨日人流亦不俗，其中熱銷書《鼎爺廚房》已售出近6,000本，成功追回因天氣因素減少的生意額，稱整體表現與去年相若。<br />\n<br />\n而中國出版商今日下午改陸續將書籍裝<br />\n<br />\n箱，部份人更已提早離場。有中國書商表示，今年書展生意減少30%，認為人流減少及讀者只買繁體字書而不買簡體字出版是銷量差的主因，籲政府應加強簡體字教育。他又指不會因銷情不理想不減價散貨，否則讀書習慣有折扣以後就員在最後一天入場，寧願付較貴運費運走剩書。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57000437&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57000437%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170725&d=k6tLU5ag40v2dGNDhWlZki7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=6e75e39f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57000437%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170725&h=22efcf95\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57000437&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170725</a>"},{"pid":"7bfdd72d4f2f6e7bc4b3db2885aa05ffdf75b20d","tid":335031,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85ac3991df28f2b6678a55b7a8f15d8051cb30a","tid":335031,"uid":51129,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:19:52.000Z","msg":"政府應制定政策助我維持銷量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如直接啲叫政府送錢比你好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" clas