割版</blockquote><br />\n呢樣先緊要，尤其文史哲類書，小小郁到大陸佬都要cut走佢<br />\n<br />\n真係比多小小買原文/ 台灣譯本好過"},{"pid":"3086f3b4cae9c879fa0943e0fa1525317b253e6b","tid":335031,"uid":72241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:11:08.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母啦 明撚知呢到個撚個用繁體字就用吓個系腦諗吓啦 係到逆水行舟 抵撚佢死啦<br />\n<br />\n唔通係佢個到賣繁體字 然後冇人買又屌9人話點解啲人唔學佢老母殘體字咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d83f631769f12e5894a6d9313adfe1310f5c75b","tid":335031,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:11:37.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b08e73806fa0f76bb6e22bf8f98a432023ee8e5","tid":335031,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:11:58.000Z","msg":"老老實實<br />\n殘體字整出嚟係俾文盲用<br />\n喺書寫方面可能係比繁體字更快更容易<br />\n寫文章可能更快<br />\n但係喺閱讀同資訊傳達方面就比繁體差好遠"},{"pid":"699af9e50bcfeedd09ba194b6b6084e503147cfc","tid":335031,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:14:22.000Z","msg":"其實簡體字都唔係問題，但紙質比繁體書差勁遠。"},{"pid":"93210c0cba8dc44a26d2befe93b709fd60ecf80f","tid":335031,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:15:47.000Z","msg":"做生意包賺架 屌你老母"},{"pid":"f45d9cfebf63efe67bc477dd7f75e88ffdfe3ae9","tid":335031,"uid":23180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:15:49.000Z","msg":"買殘體字書都唔會去呢D散貨場買啦，價錢又唔係平<br />\n<br />\n本身識正體字根本就唔會完全睇唔明殘體字<br />\n<br />\n關教育撚事咩，當香港人水魚任劏都傻傻地"},{"pid":"4f6e7bb91c12e58fbc9f9f10acc74e1239e2d825","tid":335031,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:25:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老老實實<br />\n殘體字整出嚟係俾文盲用<br />\n喺書寫方面可能係比繁體字更快更容易<br />\n寫文章可能更快<br />\n但係喺閱讀同資訊傳達方面就比繁體差好遠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要快不如拉丁化<br />\n全部寫哂拉丁拼音字母<br />\n呢個年代打字多過寫字<br />\n殘體有存在嘅必要嗎？<br />\n<br />\n再講無任何研究證實筆劃少啲，會易學咗<br />\n漢字係用圖像記憶<br />\n筆劃多少唔影響學習效率<br />\n相反部首同部件結合先係重點<br />\n<br />\n係呢一點 睇到土共劣行<br />\n同大交合一樣<br />\n永遠唔會認錯"},{"pid":"32bb747e98860befbf200fd0ffd91e7686df047b","tid":335031,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:30:34.000Z","msg":"學哂大陸思維「總之係你唔啱」"},{"pid":"c36289b353d6f755b1fab59f3a421dfa70051fe4","tid":335031,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:32:46.000Z","msg":"笑 人仔加陣升哂 返大陸書城 同香港d價差唔多計返匯率可能仲貴... 以前就貪平,但紙質又差，譯又譯得衰 今次仲要在書展賣 書展就出名平 大家一樣價點解要買簡體 on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ecfcc2112ea5017635ee2ceebcfddb08f89eec","tid":335031,"uid":6639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:35:55.000Z","msg":"唔係因應市場而改變<br />\n反而要市場改變黎遷就你<br />\n返鄉下執牛屎啦"},{"pid":"fe71fa169f2e368a4ea78f09fd57a4922ddc4bd2","tid":335031,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:37:43.000Z","msg":"等睇下年更冇人買啊屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdd294cebf7e6c5de85a53323afda6d4cd21370","tid":335031,"uid":129877,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:39:40.000Z","msg":"So9ry<br />\n有文化既人係唔撚會睇殘體"},{"pid":"5a051cd0275fa6287b6ca0fa62c9035b787c84f4","tid":335031,"uid":322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:40:31.000Z","msg":"再嘈屌你老味買英文<br />\n食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bc2f41020232637555b36634143790e7ce289a","tid":335031,"uid":28,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:41:46.000Z","msg":"醜女寫真集賣唔出既話唔通又叫政府加強性教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1464db7ba92e3a95bc2c583c6564e2681ddd742c","tid":335031,"uid":36438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:42:35.000Z","msg":"唔係唔識睇 係因為唔鍾意睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ef1d7917949fd31ccd6a11dfea3f2cb4e9be99","tid":335031,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:42:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a82580d6e710e21a365f3ccca54854a9029a762e","tid":335031,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:43:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係唔識睇 係因為唔鍾意睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係，根本個個都識睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但口味同文化呢家野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38bf9d41e82f69cc21567cca61f8ed1f1264503c","tid":335031,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:46:34.000Z","msg":"殘體書都係10蚊8蚊本<br />\n咁都賣唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37da19f2d0aa492260a1d23fa5a3dc3193b7804","tid":335031,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:47:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>午飯過後越來越多市民入場書展，有大書商指已成功收復失成，生意與去年持平。三聯書店副經理高先生表示，首兩日少人入場及颱風停市半日對銷情有負面影響，但昨日延長開放時間有助追回生意，令整個書展表現可與去年持平。<br />\n<br />\n萬里機構總經理朱素貞亦指出，颱風日書展重開後市民反應踴躍，昨日人流亦不俗，其中熱銷書《鼎爺廚房》已售出近6,000本，成功追回因天氣因素減少的生意額，稱整體表現與去年相若。<br />\n<br />\n而中國出版商今日下午改陸續將書籍裝<br />\n<br />\n箱，部份人更已提早離場。有中國書商表示，今年書展生意減少30%，認為人流減少及讀者只買繁體字書而不買簡體字出版是銷量差的主因，籲政府應加強簡體字教育。他又指不會因銷情不理想不減價散貨，否則讀書習慣有折扣以後就員在最後一天入場，寧願付較貴運費運走剩書。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57000437&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57000437%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170725&d=k6tLU5ag40v2dGNDhWlZki7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=6e75e39f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57000437%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170725&h=22efcf95\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57000437&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170725</a></blockquote><br />\n6000 本 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你香港人真係⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n鼎爺本書有咩問題？</blockquote><br />\n嗰位巴打將兩段痴埋嚟睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d18d315507acc59fd987768bda2f2989522dc7","tid":335031,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:48:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係唔識睇 係因為唔鍾意睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係，根本個個都識睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但口味同文化呢家野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有時間都睇多幾套美劇日劇啦<br />\n睇支那賤畜殘體字浪費時間咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d92fb2e0c9160a99a130e3cf00fd02c59fb222d","tid":335031,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:49:35.000Z","msg":"跌3成?<br />\n上年多啲人睇殘體?"},{"pid":"4ed751f28b9d94f3c86643fe6cb2fd5f2939428d","tid":335031,"uid":5550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:50:08.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"464c53c07d56f6485a5c009ad3056b37885c8423","tid":335031,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:51:13.000Z","msg":"簡體字書而家跟繁體字書價錢差唔多,正常來講當然港台會選返繁體字書,但簡體字書而家質素唔差,制作追得上台版一樣精美,"},{"pid":"f94123566a8f29b4f1e1b14e2dc609903e7d4230","tid":335031,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:52:01.000Z","msg":"好彩從不幫襯垃圾"},{"pid":"7ef2c14d9f6c2bd62d46